node.text:
THE INFAMOUS SMOOTHIE👇🏻:
•handful of ice
•1/2 frozen banana🍌
•1 cup frozen berries (i love blueberry🫐)
•1 scoop protein powder
•1 scoop collagen peptides
•1 tbsp ground flax seeds
•1 tbsp chia seeds
•1 tbsp MCT oil
•big a$$ spoonfuls of peanut or almond butter🥜🍯
•handful of spinach🥝 
•water or nut milk for desired thickness

blend until creamy and smooth. if you’re me add some granola on top!!! 

#smoothierecipes #smoothie #glutenfree #dairyfree

the scoop: 
•5 hard boiled eggs (cooked for 12 minutes with a splash of vinegar in water)
•1.5 tablespoons mayo
•1 teaspoon dijon mustard
•sea salt and black pepper

serve on toasted bagel with melted cheese and VOILIA!

you guys know i am so not a savory food fan first thing in the morning but i am SO a fan of savory breakfast foods for lunch or dinner🙃and this PALEO EVERYTHING BAGEL BREAD is a staple here🥯🍞it’s the best toasted with some cream cheese or avocado and lox or even just a little ghee or butter action. pair it with your eggs or really anything you want. 

this a recipe originally in my cookbook but because ily it’s also on my blog! LINK TO RECIPE IS IN MY BIO + rachlmansfield.com/the-best-paleo-everything-bagel-bread
